	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-147980" number="45150" version="2799">
			<HEADING>Chapter 21: Publication of Decisions</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-5277" name="T19C021"/>Chapter 21: Publication of Decisions</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-38192" number="45151" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 21-01 General.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-5279" name="T19C021_21-01"/>§ 21-01 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">General.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38193" number="45152" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Definition of a decision. </CHARFORMAT>A decision of the Commissioner of Finance is a report, containing findings of fact and conclusions of law, which is issued after the conclusion of a hearing before the Bureau of Hearings.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38194" number="45153" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Effect of a decision. </CHARFORMAT>A decision of the Commissioner of Finance represents the opinion of the Commissioner as to the application of the law, regulations and other precedential material to the facts presented at the hearing before the Bureau of Hearings.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-38195" number="45154" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 21-02 Publication Availability by Kinds of Proceedings.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-5281" name="T19C021_21-02"/>§ 21-02 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Publication Availability by Kinds of Proceedings.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38196" number="45155" version="1836">
									<PARA>(All statutory references are to <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Title 11</LINK> of the Administrative Code of the City of New York).</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38197" number="45156" version="2307">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Unincorporated Business Income Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C005" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 5</LINK>) and the City Business Taxes [General Corporation Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C006" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 6</LINK>, Subchapter 2), Financial Corporation Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C006" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 6</LINK>, Subchapter 3), and Transportation Corporation Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C006" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 6</LINK>, Subchapter 4)].</CHARFORMAT> All Decisions of the Commissioner of Finance pertaining to hearings concluded on and after January 1, 1988, will be published and made available to the public. Decisions issued in connection with hearings concluded prior to January 1, 1988 will also be published and made available to the public, except that the taxpayer&apos;s name, address, and other identifying information will be deleted.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38198" number="45157" version="2307">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Annual Vault Charge (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C027" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 27</LINK>), Cigarette Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C013" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 13</LINK>) and Foreign and Alien Insurers tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="t11c009" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 9</LINK>)</CHARFORMAT>. All decisions of the Commissioner of Finance will be made available to the public irrespective of the date(s) on which the hearing was held or the decision rendered.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38199" number="45158" version="2307">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Commercial Rent or Occupancy Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="t11c007" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 7</LINK>), Tax on Commercial Motor Vehicles and Motor Vehicles for Transportation of Passengers (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="t11c008" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 8</LINK>), Utility Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="t11c011" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 11</LINK>), Horse Race Admissions Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C012" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 12</LINK>), Tax on Transfer of Taxicab Licenses (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C014" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 14</LINK>), Tax on Coin Operated Amusement Devices (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="t11c015" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 15</LINK>), Real Property Transfer Tax (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C021" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 21</LINK>), Tax on Owners of Motor Vehicles (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="t11c022" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 22</LINK>), Tax on Retail Licensees of the State Liquor Authority (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C024" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 24</LINK>), and Tax on Occupancy of Hotel Rooms (<LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T11C025" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Ch. 25</LINK>). </CHARFORMAT>All decisions of the Commissioner of Finance rendered on and after January 1, 1989, will be published and made available to the public. Decisions rendered prior to January 1, 1989 will also be published and made available to the public, except that the taxpayer&apos;s name, address, and other identifying information will be deleted.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38200" number="45159" version="3">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Article 78 proceedings. </CHARFORMAT>All decisions of the Commissioner of Finance from which the taxpayer has applied for judicial review in the manner provided by Article 78 of the Civil Practice Law and Rules will be published and made available to the public, irrespective of the tax involved or the date the decision was rendered.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-38201" number="45160" version="3">
								<HEADING>§ 21-03 Requests for Copies.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-5283" name="T19C021_21-03"/>§ 21-03 <CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Requests for Copies.</CHARFORMAT>
								</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-38202" number="45161" version="3">
									<PARA>Requests for copies of decisions of the Commissioner of Finance should be made to the City of New York, Department of Finance, Hearings Bureau Disclosure Officer, 345 Adams Street, Brooklyn, N.Y. 11201.</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
